# Force LF line endings for all text files. Without this, Windows checkouts
# mix CRLF/LF and various editor/formatter quirks have produced
# duplicate-tail corruption in CI builds. Locking everything to LF makes the
# entire team / CI / Docker pipeline see byte-identical files.

* text=auto eol=lf

*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.jsx text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.scss text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf

# Binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.xlsx binary
*.docx binary
